<div class="rich-text">
  <h2>The CPA exam</h2>

  <p>
    Messiah University gives you an edge as you prepare to take the four parts of the Certified
    Public Accounting (CPA) exam. Our students have historically exceeded the national average pass
    rate for first-time test takers. They also typically complete the exam years earlier than their
    peers from other institutions. Our alumni rave about Messiah’s Accounting program and the
    advantage they received in starting their career as a CPA.
  </p>
